Package: UKTides
Title: A small package to query Admiralty Maritime Data Solutions for data on UK high & low tides
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Simon",
           family = "Tarr",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "si.tarr@outlook.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8464-1240"))
Description: This package uses the Admiralty Maritime Data Solutions API to download 7-day tide forecasts for the UK. It also includes functionality to find the nearest tide station given a lat/long point within the UK.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
